Author: edthrowaway97
Text: Talk to her first before getting your parents involved. This is a tricky one and I don't give out the best advice I admit. But if someone found out about mine I would like them to talk to me first, I mean just admit you were looking for some lipstick and accidentally came across some things that worry you and you are not being judgemental just concerned. I'm sorry you're in this situation it must be difficult. Hopefully you guys can have a long talk about everything
